###  http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#ClassC
:ClassC rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                 :RiskClass ;
        rdfs:comment "A high regulatory risk class under the IVDR framework." ;
        rdfs:label "Class C" .


###  http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#ClassIII
:ClassIII rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                   :RiskClass ;
          rdfs:comment "The highest regulatory risk class under the MDR framework." ;
          rdfs:label "Class III" .


