          rdfs:label "User Notice FSCA-009" .


###  http://www.eudamed.eu/ontology#Germany
:Germany rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                  :Country ;
         rdfs:comment "The Federal Republic of Germany, a European country." ;
         rdfs:label "Germany" .


